2.text: M y name is Viruli. I live in Panadura. I am 10 years old. My school is Mahamaya Girls' College. I am in grade 6. My hobby is gardening. I have a brother and two sisters. My mother's name is Ruwini and my father's name is Rasika. I like pink most. I have a pet dog. My favourite subject is Science. I want to be a scientist one day.

3.text: M y name is Upendran Subramaniam and I am 10 years old. I am from Jaffna. I am a grade 6 student of Jaffna College. My father is Rakesh and my mother is Parvathi. They are teachers. 4.text: I am Manuka Basuru Herath. I am 11 years old. I am studying in grade 7 at Vijayaba Vidyalaya. My family is small. I have two sisters. My mother is Kumari Herath and my father is Sampath Herath. I have a pet dog too. My hobbies are reading and writing poems. My favourite subjects are Sinhala and Science. I like to eat red rice with jak curry. My ambition is to be a writer.
